{
  "texts": [
    "Sensing expert.",
    "The sensing expert continuously takes multi-modal data as input and outputs the semantic result for the planning expert. 2.",
    "Planning expert.",
    "The planning expert, drawing on knowledge provided in the memory module, analyzes the natural-language input from the sensing expert or the coding expert, and decomposes it into a series of feasible subtasks. 3.",
    "Grounding expert."
  ]
}